      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking at some budget stuff for the city council. we need to decide where to put the new park funds in chicago. can u help me break down some of the different neighborhoods? i need to know which areas have the most need vs which areas might have more issues with community stability or crime so we can manage the risks properly. maybe focus on some of the south and west side areas vs the north side so i can see the differences.",
